       Welcome to USAID's News & Information area, which is devoted to
     delivering updated press material to the public and members of the
                                   media.

       If you are a member of the public and you have questions about
     information that you find in this area of our web site, please feel
                           free to contact us at:

                  U.S. Agency for International Development
                             Information Center
                           Ronald Reagan Building
                          Washington, DC 20523-1000

                          Telephone: (202) 712-4810
                             Fax: (202) 216-3524

    If you are a member of the press, you may contact our press relations
                                 office at:

                  U.S. Agency for International Development
                                Press Office
                           Ronald Reagan Building
                          Washington, DC 20523-6100

